Emberstorm loop
    Events
        Time - Every 0.50 seconds of game time
    Conditions
    Actions
        For each (Integer Emst_MUI3) from 1 to Emst_MUI1, do (Actions)
            Loop - Actions
                -------- Convenience integer --------
                Set VariableSet Emst_i = Emst_MUI2[Emst_MUI3]
                -------- Update --------
                Set VariableSet Emst_dur[Emst_i] = (Emst_dur[Emst_i] - 0.50)
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        (Emst_caster[Emst_i] is alive) Equal to True
                        Emst_dur[Emst_i] Greater than 0.00
                    Then - Actions
                        -------- Area damage --------
                        Set VariableSet Emst_tempp = (Position of Emst_caster[Emst_i])
                        Set VariableSet Emst_tempug = (Units within Emst_aoe[Emst_i] of Emst_tempp.)
                        Unit Group - Pick every unit in Emst_tempug and do (Actions)
                            Loop - Actions
                                Set VariableSet Emst_pickedu = (Picked unit)
                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                    If - Conditions
                                        (Emst_pickedu is Magic Immune) Equal to False
                                        (Emst_pickedu is dead) Equal to False
                                        (Emst_pickedu belongs to an enemy of (Owner of Emst_caster[Emst_i]).) Equal to True
                                    Then - Actions
                                        Unit - Cause Emst_caster[Emst_i] to damage Emst_pickedu, dealing Emst_dmg[Emst_i] damage of attack type Spells and damage type Normal
                                        Special Effect - Create a special effect attached to the origin of Emst_pickedu using Abilities\Spells\Human\Feedback\SpellBreakerAttack.mdl
                                        Special Effect - Destroy (Last created special effect)
                                    Else - Actions
                        Custom script:   call DestroyGroup(udg_Emst_tempug)
                        -------- Seven Tongues of Pytho Addition --------
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                HF_activeHellion[(Custom value of Emst_caster[Emst_i])] Equal to 3
                            Then - Actions
                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                    If - Conditions
                                        (Random real number between 0.00 and 1.00) Greater than or equal to 0.60
                                    Then - Actions
                                        Unit - Create 1 Flame Tornado for (Owner of Emst_caster[Emst_i]) at Emst_tempp facing Default building facing degrees
                                        Set VariableSet Emst_tornado = (Last created unit)
                                        Unit - Set level of Emberstorm Immolation  for Emst_tornado to (Level of Hellion: Emberstorm  for Emst_caster[Emst_i])
                                        Unit - Add a (Random real number between 3.00 and 5.00) second Generic expiration timer to (Last created unit)
                                    Else - Actions
                            Else - Actions
                        Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_Emst_tempp)
                    Else - Actions
                        -------- Recycle indices --------
                        Set VariableSet Emst_MUI2[Emst_MUI3] = Emst_MUI2[Emst_MUI1]
                        Set VariableSet Emst_MUI2[Emst_MUI1] = Emst_i
                        Set VariableSet Emst_MUI1 = (Emst_MUI1 - 1)
                        Set VariableSet Emst_MUI3 = (Emst_MUI3 - 1)
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                Emst_MUI1 Equal to 0
                            Then - Actions
                                Trigger - Turn off (This trigger)
                            Else - Actions
